originalText.text:
I showed up for my second appointment 10 minutes early. I texted him, texted him again, called... Half an hour after my appointment was supposed to begin, the secretary walked over and informed me Dr Pasculli was in his office with someone else.

The hilarious part of this is Dr Pasculli had no problem taking a minute out of my first meeting with him to let another client know over text that we were running a few minutes late.

I strongly recommend you do not put your mental health in this person's hands. Find somebody who values your time instead.
